/*
  Macro created to add delta animations to something. Much like a "self-delta sequence"
	This macro was created with the intention of recreating as corrective animations of l4d and l4d2 for Francis (biker) and Zoey (teenangst)
*/
$definemacro ArkjDLCMacro filename activity \\
$sequence $filename$ $filename$ subtract $filename$ 0 delta activity ACT_$activity$ -1 \\
$continue $filename$ \\
